### Who am I ?
I'm a Software Engineer who was born in Cairo, Egypt and moved to the States in 2005.
I love writing software and working with new technology. [Check out](http://github.com/jvshahid) what I've been working
on.

### My resume
Have some opennings and want to know if I'm a good fit ? Take a look at [my resume](http://jvshahid.github.com/Resume).
My resume has the most recent contact info. Drop me an email if you want to talk.
